OL,3,CRoyal Marines line street to pay
OL,4,Ctribute to Second World War veteran
OL,6,FWatch: ITV Meridian's Sally Simmonds
OL,7,Freports from Salisbury.
OL,9,FHundreds of people have paid their
OL,10,Frespects to one of the last remaining
OL,11,FRoyal Marine veterans of the Second
OL,12,FWorld War.
OL,14,FA street in Salisbury was lined by
OL,15,Fmourners at the funeral of Jim Wren,
OL,16,Fwho died earlier this year aged 105.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
