OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772705110
OL,3,CRoyal Marines line street to pay
OL,4,Ctribute to Second World War veteran
OL,6,FThe ceremony was attended by family,
OL,7,Ffriends, and well-wishers and his
OL,8,Fcoffin was draped in a Royal Marine
OL,9,FCorps Flag as it was carried into St
OL,10,FThomas's Church by servicemen to
OL,11,Fcomplete silence.
OL,13,FDuring the service, he was described
OL,14,Fby his family as a "passive man who
OL,15,Fwould never get angry" and who rarely
OL,16,Fspoke about his service, "only opening
OL,17,Fup in recent years".
OL,26,@vD@TOUwD@VO]xD@ZOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
