CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772705110
OL,3,CRoyal Marines line street to pay
OL,4,Ctribute to Second World War veteran
OL,6,FThe service ended to the sound of
OL,7,Fbugles as members of the Royal Marines
OL,8,Fand his family paid their final
OL,9,Ffarewells.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
